Class
Description
CrossoverAlternate
The class CrossoverOperators contains methods for performing alternate crossover between parents

The class CrossoverOperators contains methods for performing random crossover between parents

The class CrossoverOperators contains methods for performing Single Point crossover between parents
Fitness
The class Fitness has calculateFitness methods to calculate fitness score for a Population or an Individual
GACreator
The class GANaiveCreator will use operator factory to create and return a GeneticAlgorithm object.

The class GANaiveCreator will use naive operator factory to create and return a GeneticAlgorithm object.
GANaiveOperatorFactory
The class @code GANaiveOperatorFactory contains methods for performing basic Selection, Crossover and Mutation functions
GAOptimisedCreator
The class GANaiveCreator will use optimised operator factory to create and return a GeneticAlgorithm object.
GAOptimisedOperatorFactory
The class @code GAOptimisedOperatorFactory contains methods for performing basic Selection, Crossover and Mutation functions
GARandomCreator
The class GANaiveCreator will use random operator factory to create and return a GeneticAlgorithm object.
GARandomOperatorFactory
The class @code GARandomOperatorFactory contains methods for performing random Selection, Crossover and Mutation functions
GeneticAlgorithm
The class @code GeneticAlgorithm contains method for generating next generation of individuals
ICrossover
The interface ICrossover contains method for selecting parents
IGAOperatorFactory
The interface IGAOperatorFactory contains methods for performing basic Selection, Crossover and Mutation functions whose implementations are present in GANaiveOperatorFactory, GARandomFactory and GAOptimisedOperatorFaactory classes
IMutation
The interface IMutation contains method for mutation of children
Individual
The class Individual stores array of chromosomes and declares fitnessScore = -1.
IndividualComparator
The class IndividualComparator is used to sort population array.
ISelection
The interface ISelection contains method for selecting parents
Main
The class Main contains main method
MutationRandom
The class MutationRandom contains method for mutating children
Population
The class Population stores ArrayList of population.
SelectionElite
The class SelectionElite contains method for selecting parents
SelectionRandom
The class SelectionRandom contains method for selecting parents using a random selection
SelectionTournament
The class SelectionTournament contains method for selecting parents using a tournament based selection
